<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Appointment Letter</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .text-center { text-align: center; }
        .text-right { text-align: right; }
        .font-bold { font-weight: bold; }
        .green { color: #004d40; }
        .red { color: #b71c1c; }
        .header-title { font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .header-subtitle { font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 2px; }
        .header-subsubtitle { font-size: 11px; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .header-registrar { font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        
        .header-grid { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .header-grid td { vertical-align: top; }
        .col-left { width: 33%; font-size: 10px; line-height: 1.3; }
        .col-middle { width: 34%; text-align: center; }
        .col-right { width: 33%; font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.3; }
        
        .role-title { font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold; color: #b71c1c; margin-bottom: 2px; }
        .person-name { font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 2px; }
        
        .dotted-line { border-bottom: 1px dotted #000; display: inline-block; }
        
        .separator { border-top: 1px solid #ccc; margin: 15px 0; }
        
        .address-block { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        
        .memo-title { text-align: center; text-decoration: underline; font-weight: bold; margin: 25px 0 15px; font-size: 12px; }
        
        .list-item { margin-bottom: 15px; display: table; width: 100%; }
        .list-number { display: table-cell; width: 30px; vertical-align: top; font-weight: bold; }
        .list-content { display: table-cell; vertical-align: top; text-align: justify; }
        
        .signature-block { margin-top: 30px; }
        .signature-img { height: 40px; margin-bottom: 5px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="text-center">
        <div class="font-bold green header-title">JOSEPH SARWUAN TARKA UNIVERSITY</div>
        <div class="font-bold header-subtitle">MAKURDI - NIGERIA</div>
        <div class="header-subsubtitle">(Formerly FEDERAL UNIVERSITY OF AGRICULTURE, MAKURDI)</div>
        <div class="font-bold red header-registrar">OFFICE OF THE REGISTRAR</div>
    </div>
    
    <table class="header-grid">
        <tr>
            <td class="col-left">
                <div class="role-title">VICE-CHANCELLOR:</div>
                <div class="person-name">Eng. Professor Isaac N. Itodo</div>
                <div>FNSE, FNIAE, FSES, FAEng, NPOM</div>
                <div>BEng (Jos), MSc (Ibadan), PhD (Ibadan)</div>
                <br>
                <div class="role-title">REGISTRAR:</div>
                <div class="person-name">Dr. John Ujo David</div>
                <div>B.A (Jos), MPIA (Lagos), Ph.D (BSU)</div>
                <div>FCIA, ANUPA, mni, MNIM, MHSN</div>
                <br>
                <div class="font-bold" style="margin-top: 5px;">Our Ref: &nbsp;<span class="dotted-line">{{ $reference }}</span></div>
            </td>
            <td class="col-middle">
                <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Logo" style="height: 110px;">
            </td>
            <td class="col-right">
                <div class="font-bold">Private Mail Bag 2373</div>
                <div>Makurdi, Nigeria</div>
                <div>Tel: +234 803 812 4991</div>
                <div>E-mail: registrar@uam.edu.ng<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;registrar@gmail.com</div>
                <div>http://www.uam.edu.ng</div>
                <br><br>
                <div class="font-bold">Date: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="dotted-line" style="min-width: 120px; text-align: center;">{{ $date }}</span></div>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    <div class="separator"></div>
    
    <div class="address-block">
        {{ $name }},<br>
        {{ $address_line_1 }}<br>
        {{ $address_line_2 }}
    </div>
    
    <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
        Dear <strong>{{ $firstName }}</strong>,
    </div>
    
    <div class="memo-title">
        MEMORANDUM OF APPOINTMENT TO ACADEMIC POSITION
    </div>
    
    <div class="list-item">
        <div class="list-number">1.</div>
        <div class="list-content">
            I write on the directive of the Vice-Chancellor, Joseph Sarwuan Tarka University, Makurdi and on behalf of Council to offer you an appointment as <strong>{{ $role }}</strong> on <strong>{{ $grade }}</strong> in <strong>{{ $department }}</strong>, Joseph Sarwuan Tarka University, Makurdi.
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="list-item">
        <div class="list-number">2.</div>
        <div class="list-content">
            The appointment is subject to the provisions of the University Laws, Statutes and Ordinances made thereunder, and to regulations governing the conditions of appointment of staff as may be approved by the University Council from time to time.
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="list-item">
        <div class="list-number">3.</div>
        <div class="list-content">
            The appointment is also subject to your being declared medically fit on submission of a medical report of fitness from the University Health Services.
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="list-item">
        <div class="list-number">4.</div>
        <div class="list-content">
            You will be required to perform your duties diligently, support the mandate of the University, and carry out other assignments as may be assigned to you by your Head of Department or the University Administration.
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="list-item">
        <div class="list-number">5.</div>
        <div class="list-content">
            Please indicate your acceptance or otherwise of this offer within six (6) weeks from the date of this letter. If you accept the offer, return a signed copy of this memorandum to the Registrar.
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div style="margin-top: 20px; font-weight: bold;">
        Congratulations!
    </div>
    
    <div class="signature-block">
        <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Signature" class="signature-img"><br>
        <strong>Dr. John U. David,</strong> <span style="font-size: 9px;">FCIA</span><br>
        <em>Registrar</em>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
